Package: jointSeg
Type: Package
Title: Joint segmentation of multivariate (copy number) signals
Version: 0.4.1
Date: 2014-02-13
Author: Morgane Pierre-Jean and Pierre Neuvial
Maintainer: Morgane Pierre-Jean <morgane.pierrejean@genopole.cnrs.fr>
Description: This package implements functions to quickly segment multivariate signals into piecewise constant profiles. A typical application is the joint segmentation of total DNA copy numbers and allelic ratios obtained from Single Nucleotide Polymorphism (SNP) microarrays in cancer studies.
License: LGPL (>= 2.1)
Depends: R (>= 2.10), matrixStats (>= 0.6.0), acnr (>= 0.1.3)
Suggests: cghseg, DNAcopy, PSCBS, aroma.light, R.cache, digest, changepoint (>= 1.0.2), CnaStruct

